st covenant had been faultless, there would have been no occasion for a second one. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:8:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But finding fault with his people, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit with them"},{"kind":"text","text":" he says: "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Other mss read finding fault, he says to them"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit with them"},{"marker":2,"text":"Other mss read finding fault, he says to them"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:8:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"not like the covenant"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:8:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For this is the covenant"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:8:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And each person will not teach his fellow citizen,"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss read neighbor"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss read neighbor"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:8:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For I will forgive their wrongdoing,"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:8:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"By saying a new covenant, he has declared that the first is obsolete. And what is obsolete and growing old is about to pass away. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 5:17","book":"2Co","chapter":5,"verse":17,"letter":"a"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Co 5:17","book":"2Co","chapter":5,"verse":17}],"footnotes":[]}]},"cachedAt":1783279679795}